| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4664 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomcortex)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 87abc9c2-b717-5fba-97d2-646d936f8f8f"
